_json.description: AWESOME Tutorial for Solid Maple DIY Wood Countertops in a Kitchen.  Learn how to build wood counters the CORRECT WAY so they last - no warping or splitting. This post takes you through, step by step, how to build DIY wood countertops and shares tips on woodworking and wood movement. These maple DIY solid wood countertops are stained white, but you can choose any color. You'll also find out how to seal a wood countertop and how to make wood countertops waterproof. #diycounters #woodcountertops
